	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay...as far as weapon skills go...if you touch anything but two handed slashing (okay maybe two handed bash...) your gonna get laughed at by the other trolls...<br><br>I have 3 hot keys, sense head, bash, taunt...I just drum my fingers on em during combat...easy to keep it all maxed...<br><br>swimming...me never tell you dis...but trollies<br>can't drown in da creek in Grobb just before swamp...swim into corner...while dere...practice<br>your fletching ;)<br><br>get a carved elm bow (better yet, MAKE your own<br>carved elm bow...med nock, wood shaft, round fletch, field points arrows will be your mainstay) it shots for 10 and has a delay of only 39...with SOW you should be able to get a shot or two off per combat...but archery will STILL be slow...<br><br>good luck brother!<br>&nbsp;<br>Krilmar<br>Troll Shadow Knight<br>Master Blacksmith <br>(scary...ain't it)</td></tr>
