	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ogre and Troll SKs almost exclusivly use 2hs.&nbsp;&nbsp;Feel free to keep your others maxed also, but 2hs is your mainstay, it should be maxed at ALL times, so you can switch to it in a hairy fight to dish out the damage.  As a large race, you can use 2hs and still Bash (slam), so this is your best weapon skill, as we do not get dual wield, or kick, or any other fancy melee skills. Leave the one handed weapons to us puny SKs who need to have a shield.<br><br>Soulslicer Hatebringer<br>Dark Elf SK level 40<br>Erollisi Marr<br>Proud member of Shadowspawn<br>&nbsp;<br>Soulslicer, Shadowknight of Shadowspawn.<br>Evil will always Triumph because good... is Dumb</td></tr>
